on%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKyle%20Gow%2C%20venue%20manager%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmws.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Vault%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20members-only%20venue%20in%20Edinburgh%2C%20told%20BI%20some%20of%20their%20members%20use%20their%20bottle%20keep%20to%20impress%20guests%20and%20business%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20want%20to%20show%20off%20what%20they've%20got.%20People%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20buy%20a%20more%20expensive%20bottle%20to%20put%20in%20the%20bottle%20keep%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20status%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Gow%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20clients%20purchase%20desirable%20bottles%20of%20whisky%20that%20they%20can%20later%20flex%20to%20friends%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20buy%20the%20same%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20members%20buy%20some%20exclusive%20bottles%2C%20come%20in%20and%20do%20exactly%20that%20%E2%80%94%20show%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20way%20for%20establishments%20like%20these%20to%20get%20to%20know%20its%20clientele%20better%2C%20Gow%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20a%20regular%20client%20is%20always%20looking%20for%20the%20next%20bottle%20to%20put%20in%20their%20locker%20so%20they%20don't%20lose%20their%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'd%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20his%20bottle%20for%20him%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20knew%20it%20was%20getting%20low%20we'd%20be%20like%2C%20'This%20is%20what%20we%20think%20for%20the%20next%20one%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20venue%20has%20120%20spaces%20for%20bottles%2C%20Gow%20told%20BI%20they%20have%20been%20extremely%20popular%20and%20they're%20quickly%20running%20out%20of%20space.%20However%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20liquor%20lockers%20globally%20means%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20options%20to%20choose%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vaultsteakhouse.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVault%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theflatironroom.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Flatiron%20Room%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20New%20York%20both%20have%20extensive%20whiskey%20collections%20waiting%20to%20be%20kept%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20luxury%20of%20choice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGow%20told%20BI%20that%20most%20of%20their%20clientele%20know%20what%20they%20like%20to%20drink%2C%20so%20it%20can%20be%20more%20economical%20to%20buy%20a%20bottle%20than%20individual%20servings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20an%20average%20bottle%20of%20whisky%20can%20cost%20%C2%A375%20plus%20the%20%C2%A330%20cost%20to%20keep%20a%20bottle%20in%20the%20locker%20for%20six%20months%2C%20which%20adds%20up%20to%20around%20%24130.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20are%20roughly%2028%20servings%20of%20whisky%20in%20an%20average-size%20bottle%2C%20and%20if%20purchased%20individually%20would%20cost%20around%20%C2%A3273%2C%20or%20around%20%24350.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20clientele%20dropping%20thousands%20on%20memberships%20at%20members'%20clubs%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20they%20save%20with%20a%20bottle%20keep%20likely%20isn't%20their%20reason%20for%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20talking%20about%20luxury%20travel%20or%20hospitality%2C%20%26quot%3Bchoice%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20overused%20buzzword.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20bottle%20keep%2C%20not%20everyone%20needs%20a%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20or%20wants%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliquor-lockers-bar-members-club-bottle-keep-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705667227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6571f5fc0ec98e92f74d25d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h