A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20could%20see%20its%20first%20trillionaire%20with%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20according%20to%20assessment%20of%20global%20inequalities%20published%20earlier%20this%20week%20by%20UK-based%20non-profit%20Oxfam%20International.%20The%20report%20also%20notes%20that%20ending%20poverty%20-%20the%20target%20for%20which%20is%202030%20under%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20-%20may%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20another%20229%20years.%20According%20to%20Time%20Magazine%2C%20the%20world%20got%20its%20first%20billionaire%20in%201916%2C%20when%20John%20D%20Rockefeller%20achieved%20the%20status%20largely%20through%20his%20ownership%20of%20Standard%20Oil.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20ultra%20rich%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20systemic%20exploitation%20lurking%20behind%20the%20widening%20wealth%20gap%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20the%20criticism%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20has%20only%20widened.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oxfam.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2Fwealth-five-richest-men-doubles-2020-five-billion-people-made-poorer-decade-division%5C%22%3EOxfam%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20world's%20five%20richest%20people%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20their%20wealth%20since%202020.%20These%20are%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20LVMH%20owner%20Bernard%20Arnault%2C%20Amazon%20founder%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20Oracle%20founder%20Larry%20Ellison%20and%20investor%20Warren%20Buffett.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20their%20names%20have%20been%20highlighted%20in%20the%20Oxfam%20report%2C%20several%20outlets%20-%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2024%2F01%2F19%2Foxfam-world-first-trillionaire-musk-arnault-bezos-ellison-buffett%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFortune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fmoney%2F2024%2F01%2F17%2Fworld-first-trillionaire-oxfam-wealth-disparity-report%2F72255512007%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20are%20claiming%20that%20one%20of%20them%20could%20reach%20the%20trillionaire%20status.%20The%20analysis%20is%20based%20on%20Forbes%20data%20that%20shows%20Mr%20Musk%20is%20on%20top%20with%20a%20wealth%20of%20%24226.6%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes'%20real-time%20rankings%20released%20on%20Wednesday.%20Bernard%20Arnault%20and%20his%20family%20own%20%24175.1%20billion%2C%20followed%20by%20Jeff%20Bezos%20with%20%24173.6%20billion%2C%20Larry%20Ellison%20with%20%24134.9%20billion%20and%20Warren%20buffet%20with%20%24119.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOxfam%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bsupercharged%26quot%3B%20surge%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20wealthy%20in%20the%20last%20three%20year%20has%20meant%20that%20billionaires%20are%20%243.3%20billion%20richer%20than%20in%202020%2C%20their%20wealth%20growing%20three%20times%20faster%20than%20the%20rate%20of%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20showed%20that%20nearly%20five%20billion%20people%20worldwide%20were%20made%20poorer%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20tax%20laws%2C%20monopolies%20and%20deregulation%20ensure%20that%20the%20cash%20is%20funnelled%20into%20pockets%20of%20the%20wealthy%20elite%2C%20%26quot%3Bbillions%20of%20people%20(are)%20shouldering%20the%20economic%20shockwaves%20of%20pandemic%2C%20inflation%20and%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Oxfam%20International%20Interim%20Executive%20Director%20Amitabh%20Behar%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20inequality%20is%20no%20accident.%20The%20billionaire%20class%20is%20ensuring%20corporations%20deliver%20more%20wealth%20to%20them%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20everyone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Behar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20imbalance%2C%20Oxfam%20called%20for%20a%20wealth%20tax%20on%20the%20world's%20millionaires%20and%20billionaires%20that%20it%20says%20could%20bring%20in%20%241.8%20trillion%20dollars%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charity%20also%20called%20to%20cap%20CEO%20pay%20and%20break%20up%20private%20monopolies%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705666620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fjc2nlbvg_elon-musk_625x300_06_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fworld-may-gets-its-first-trillionaire-in-a-decade-here-are-5-probables-4893068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Oxfam%20report%20said%20that%20the%20world's%20five%20richest%20people%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20their%20wealth%20since%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fworld-may-gets-its-first-trillionaire-in-a-decade-here-are-5-probables-4893068%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fworld-may-gets-its-first-trillionaire-in-a-decade-here-are-5-probables-4893068%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fworld-may-gets-its-first-trillionaire-in-a-decade-here-are-5-probables-4893068%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thomas%20Kwoyelo%3A%20Ugandan%20Lord's%20Resistance%20Army%20rebel%20commander%20on%20trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705666518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FFC54%2Fproduction%2F_132369546_gettyimages-633297796.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68025152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20child%20soldier%20Thomas%20Kwoyelo%20faces%20more%20than%2090%20charges%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20rape.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68025152%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68025152.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68025152.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22See%20video%3A%20Hema%20Malini%20heads%20to%20Ayodhya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705666358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106991445%2Cimgsize-60718.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhema-malini-to-perform-at-ram-temple-inauguration-in-ayodhya-mumbai-airport%2Farticleshow%2F106991445.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106991445.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActress%20and%20classical%20dancer%20Hema%20Malini%20is%20set%20to%20enchant%20audiences%20with%20a%20special%20performance%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20the%20event%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20host%20celebrities%20from%20diverse%20fields.%20Hema%20Malini%2C%20spotted%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20radiated%20simplicity%20in%20a%20peach-colored%20suit%20as%20she%20embarked%20on%20her%20journey.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20upcoming%20performance%2C%20she%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20being%20part%20of%20a%2010-day%20program%20organized%20by%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20spiritual%20essence%20of%20Bollywood%20celebrating%20Lord%20Ram.%20The%20occasion%20marks%20the%20installation%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20Lalla's%20idol%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%2C%20drawing%20the%20presence%20of%20eminent%20personalities%20like%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Anushka%20Sharma%2C%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%2C%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%20and%20Amitabh%20Bachchan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhema-malini-to-perform-at-ram-temple-inauguration-in-ayodhya-mumbai-airport%2Farticleshow%2F106991445.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEntire%20Idea%20Must%20Be%20Abandoned%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%20On%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20today%20opposed%20what%20it%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bundemocratic%26quot%3B%20idea%20of%20holding%20simultaneous%20polls%20-%20referring%20to%20the%20BJP's%20push%20for%20the%20'one%20nation%20one%20election'%20system%20-%20and%20criticised%20the%20idea%20as%20one%20that%20goes%20against%20federalism%20and%20the%20Constitution's%20basic%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20called%20for%20disbanding%20the%20committee%20that%20is%20studying%20whether%20the%20'one%20nation%20one%20election'%20system%20can%20be%20applied%20in%20a%20nation%20of%20140%20crore%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20is%20strongly%20opposed%20to%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'.%20For%20the%20sake%20of%20maintaining%20a%20thriving%20and%20a%20robust%20democracy%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20entire%20idea%20must%20be%20abandoned%20and%20the%20high-powered%20committee%20dissolved%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Niten%20Chandra%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20heads%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20in%20the%20letter%20asked%20the%20former%20President%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20allow%20his%20persona%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20former%20President%20of%20India%20to%20be%20abused%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20subvert%20the%20Constitution%20and%20parliamentary%20democracy%20in%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20on%20October%2018%2C%202023%20had%20asked%20the%20public%20to%20send%20suggestions.%20Pointing%20at%20this%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20alleged%20the%20committee%20seems%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Balready%20made%20up%20its%20mind%20and%20seeking%20a%20consultation%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20eye%20wash%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%2C%20parliament%20and%20ECI%20(Election%20Commission%20of%20India)%20should%20work%20together%20to%20ensure%20the%20people's%20mandate%20is%20respected%20rather%20than%20divert%20people's%20attention%20by%20talking%20about%20undemocratic%20ideas%20like%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20committee%20is%20%26quot%3Bbiased%26quot%3B.%20The%20committee%20was%20formed%20without%20discussion%20with%20Opposition%20parties%20that%20are%20in%20power%20in%20many%20states%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20adding%20these%20states%20will%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20decisions%20taken%20by%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20committee%20is%20headed%20by%20no%20less%20than%20the%20former%20President%20of%20India%2C%20it%20is%20distressing%20when%20even%20common%20voters%20feel%20the%20consultations%20of%20the%20committee%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20pretence%20since%20minds%20have%20already%20been%20made%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bamused%26quot%3B%20to%20hear%20the%20argument%20that%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20will%20result%20in%20financial%20savings.%20He%20said%20the%20expenses%20on%20elections%20are%20less%20than%200.02%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20Union%20Budget%20for%20the%20preceding%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20the%20people%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20consider%20this%20small%20amount%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20to%20uphold%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20website%20on%20'one%20nation%20one%20election'%20said%20the%20national%20and%20state%20elections%20were%20mostly%20held%20simultaneously%20from%201951-52%20to%201967%2C%20after%20which%20this%20cycle%20got%20broken%20and%20now%2C%20elections%20are%20held%20almost%20every%20year%20and%20within%20a%20year%20too%20at%20different%20times%2C%20which%20result%20in%20massive%20expenditure%20by%20the%20government%20and%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20diversion%20of%20security%20forces%20and%20other%20electoral%20officers%20engaged%20in%20such%20elections%20from%20their%20primary%20duties%20for%20significantly%20prolonged%20periods%2C%20and%20disruption%20in%20developmental%20work%20on%20account%20of%20prolonged%20application%20of%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'one%20nation%20one%20election'%20committee's%20terms%20of%20reference%20includes%20checking%20whether%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%20needed%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20would%20need%20ratification%20by%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705666260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8ejs001o_rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-idea-must-be-abandoned-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-on-one-nation-one-election-4892949%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20today%20opposed%20what%20it%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bundemocratic%26quot%3B%20idea%20of%20holding%20simultaneous%20polls%20-%20referring%20to%20the%20BJP's%20push%20for%20the%20'one%20nation%20one%20election'%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-idea-must-be-abandoned-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-on-one-nation-one-election-4892949%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-idea-must-be-abandoned-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-on-one-nation-one-election-4892949%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-idea-must-be-abandoned-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-on-one-nation-one-election-4892949%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gen%20Z%20is%20prioritizing%20living%20over%20working%20because%20they've%20seen%20'the%20legacy%20of%20broken%20promises'%20in%20corporate%20America%2C%20a%20future-of-work%20expert%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gen%20Zer%20working%20on%20a%20computer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aa41af6979d73718249032%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224451%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGen%20Z%20workers%20are%20prioritizing%20their%20personal%20lives%20and%20well-being%20over%20working.%20%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Starkova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20future-of-work%20expert%20said%20Gen%20Z%20%26quot%3Bwork%20to%20live%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20watched%20older%20generations%20suffer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESpeaking%20to%20Business%20Insider%20at%20Davos%2C%20Ravin%20Jesuthasan%20said%20Gen%20Z%20doesn't%20see%20the%20same%20rewards%20for%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20put%20work%20first%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20their%20personal%20life%20and%20wellbeing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20is%20choosing%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20to%20live''%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Blive%20to%20work%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20generations%20before%20them%20because%20they're%20reaping%20fewer%20rewards%20for%20their%20hard%20work%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20the%20future%20of%20work%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavin%20Jesuthasan%2C%20global%20leader%20for%20transformation%20services%20at%20consulting%20giant%20Mercer%2C%20and%20future-of-work%20expert%2C%20spoke%20to%20BI%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20this%20week%2C%20and%20he%20touched%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20Gen%20Z%20in%20the%20workplace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJesuthasan%20explained%20that%20Gen%20Z%20%26quot%3Bhas%20some%20very%20different%20attitudes%20to%20work%26quot%3B%20than%20older%20generations%20because%20they're%20one%20of%20the%20first%20generations%20that%20won't%20have%20wealth%20that%20is%20greater%20than%20that%20of%20their%20parents%20or%20grandparents.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20have%20already%20experienced%20huge%20disruptions%20like%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20have%20more%20of%20an%20attitude%20of%20work%20to%20live%20as%20opposed%20to%20live%20to%20work%20that%20many%20of%20us%20grew%20up%20with.%20This%20is%20particularly%20true%20in%20the%20West.%20They%20have%20seen%20the%20legacy%20of%20all%20these%20broken%20promises.%20In%20the%20old%20days%20and%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20West%2C%20they%20would%20promise%20you%20if%20you%20worked%20for%2030%20years%2C%20you%20have%20this%20defined%20benefit%20pension%2C%20you%20have%20retiree%20medical%20care%20etc.%20None%20of%20that%20exists%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20they've%20seen%20that%20get%20taken%20away%20from%20their%20parents%20or%20grandparents%2C%20and%20now%20there's%20a%20sense%20of%20'I'm%20only%20as%20good%20as%20the%20skills%20I%20have.%20I'm%20only%20as%20good%20as%20the%20value%20I'm%20delivering%20today%20and%20so%20these%20are%20the%20terms%20under%20which%20I%20want%20to%20work%2C%20and%20you%20either%20meet%20them%20or%20not.'%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20have%20watched%20on%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-parents-debt-jobs-wages-homeownership-social-security-retirement-economy-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillennials%20struggled%20through%20economic%20hardships%20%3C%2Fa%3Eincluding%20multiple%20recessions%20and%20a%20pandemic%20which%20have%20put%20a%20dent%20in%20their%20income%20and%20dreams%20of%20home%20ownership.%20The%20increased%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20skyrocketing%20house%20prices%2C%20and%20student%20debt%20has%20locked%20millennials%20out%20of%20the%20housing%20market%20and%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20accumulate%20wealth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-quiet-quitting-work-ethic-millennials-money-struggles-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGen%20Zers%20are%20quiet%20quitting%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20taking%20a%20step%20back%20at%20work%20because%20they're%20painfully%20aware%20that%20their%20hard%20work%20could%20essentially%20amount%20to%20nothing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20us%20built%2C%20whether%20it's%20bought%20homes%20or%20whatever%2C%20based%20on%20this%20promise%20of%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20Jesuthasan%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20this%20expectation%20that%20the%20tail%20was%20bigger.%20And%20we%20took%20on%20liabilities%20and%20obligations%20early%20on%20because%20of%20that%20tail.%20I%20think%20this%20generation%20has%20seen%20that%20tail%20dissipate.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20will%20have%20to%20start%20meeting%20people%20on%20their%20individual%20terms%20rather%20than%20taking%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%2C%20Jesuthasan%20said.%20This%20includes%20being%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bpick%20and%20choose%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bportfolio%20of%20rewards.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20has%20often%20received%20flak%20for%20their%20flippant%20attitude%20to%20work%2C%20with%20one%20survey%20last%20year%20finding%20that%2074%25%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-managers-employees-most-challenging-technological-skills-survey-2023-4%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanagers%20say%20they're%20the%20most%20challenging%20generation%20to%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw