ety%2C%20and%20commended%20the%20ANC%20Youth%20League%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enca.com%2Ftop-stories%2Fanc-youth-league-wants-more-young-people-parliament%5C%22%3Efor%20their%20inputs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20shaping%20the%20statement.%20He%20promised%20that%20the%20party%20would%20attend%20to%20their%20concerns%20and%20recommendations%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ebeneficiation%20of%20raw%20materials%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ereindustrialisation%20of%20the%20economy%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ethe%20energy%20crisis%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ethe%20climate%20crisis%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ethe%20quality%20of%20public%20services.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20items%20are%20already%20on%20the%20ANC%E2%80%99s%20policy%20programme%20being%20implemented%20in%20government.%20So%20if%20the%20party%20had%20been%20more%20astute%2C%20the%20January%208%20statement%20could%20have%20indicated%2C%20especially%20to%20its%20younger%20constituency%2C%20what%20would%20be%20done%20differently%20this%20time%20round.%20As%20it%20is%2C%20these%20items%20also%20feature%20high%20on%20the%20list%20of%20priorities%20of%20other%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20those%20formed%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBravado%20amid%20disillusionment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ANC%2C%20through%20its%20January%208%20statement%2C%20put%20on%20a%20show%20of%20bravado.%20However%2C%20it%20would%20be%20foolhardy%20of%20it%20to%20ignore%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20political%20terrain%20has%20shifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20long-serving%20members%20within%20its%20ranks%20have%20become%20disillusioned%20with%20the%20party%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politicsweb.co.za%2Fdocuments%2Fwhy-i-am-resigning-from-the-anc--mavuso-msimang%5C%22%3Eresignation%20of%20ANC%20veteran%20Mavuso%20Msimang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20later%20retracted%20his%20decision.%20Not%20all%20of%20these%20can%20be%20labelled%20rogue%20ex-me