t%20specify%20if%20said%20structure%20was%20a%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20called%20the%20razing%20of%20the%20mosque%20in%201992%20-%20followed%20by%20riots%20in%20which%20over%202%2C000%20people%20were%20killed%20-%20a%20%26quot%3Bcalculated%20act%20of%20destroying%20a%20place%20of%20public%20worship%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20the%20Muslim%20community%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bwrongly%20deprived%20of%20a%20mosque%20constructed%20well%20over%20450%20years%20ago%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-verdict-disputed-land-to-be-handed-over-to-government-trust-for-temple-sunni-board-to-get-su-2129778%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20Disputed%20Land%20To%20Be%20Given%20For%20Temple%2C%20Says%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%201%2C045-page%20judgement%20the%20court%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3B...on%20a%20balance%20of%20probabilities%2C%20the%20evidence%20of%20possessory%20claim%20of%20the%20Hindus...stands%20on%20a%20better%20footing%20than%20the%20evidence%20given%20by%20the%20Muslims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%C2%A0ordered%20that%20a%20five-acre%20%26quot%3Bsuitable%26quot%3B%20plot%20of%20land%20be%20awarded%20to%20the%20Sunni%20Waqf%20Board.%20This%2C%20the%20judges%20said%2C%20was%20to%20acknowledge%20a%20wrong%20had%20been%20committed%20and%20remedial%20action%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-case-judges-decided-to-have-judgement-of-the-court-chief-justice-4782061%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20Case%20Judges%20Opted%20For%20%26quot%3BJudgment%20Of%20The%20Court%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20exception%20of%20Mr%20Chandrachud%2C%20all%20those%20on%20that%20bench%20have%20since%20retired.Mr%20Gogoi%20is%20now%20a%20Rajya%20Sab