the%20graduates%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%20have%20made%20valuable%20and%20significant%20contributions%20to%20American%20society%20across%20many%20professions%20and%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20noted%20that%20it%20is%20the%20sense%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20to%20recognise%20the%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%20and%20significant%20contributions%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20to%20American%20society%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20House%20must%20honor%20the%20technology%2C%20scientific%2C%20and%20economic%20innovation%20attributable%20to%20graduates%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20urged%20all%20Americans%20to%20recognise%20the%20contributions%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20and%20to%20appreciate%20the%20role%20that%20Indian%20Americans%20have%20played%20in%20helping%20to%20advance%20and%20enrich%20American%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20submitted%20by%20Mr%20S%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%20further%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWhereas%20the%20presence%20of%20Indian-American%20residents%20deeply%20enriches%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20Indian-American%20community%20and%20the%20graduates%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20in%20the%20United%20States%20have%20made%20valuable%20and%20%C2%A0significant%20contributions%20to%20society%20across%20many%20professions%20and%20disciplines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20added%20that%20the%20two%20nations%20have%20affirmed%20that%20technology%20will%20play%20the%20defining%20role%20in%20deepening%20their%20partnership.%20%26quot%3BThe%20IIT%20graduates%20are%20highly%20committed%20and%20dedicated%20to%20research%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20promotion%20of%20trade%20and%20international%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705665120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fiog