rture.%20The%20immediate%20aftermath%20was%20a%20strained%20silence%20between%20Kristil%20and%20me%2C%20a%20palpable%20divide%20that%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffather-daughter-relationship-complicated-food-love-language-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eour%20relationship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20that%20day%2C%20Kristil%20and%20I%20had%20enjoyed%20a%20typical%20Parisian%20day%2C%20strolling%20through%20the%20Left%20Bank%2C%20sipping%20lattes%20and%20lost%20in%20conversation.%20These%20moments%20were%20precious%20and%20rare%2C%20as%20I%20could%20only%20visit%20Kristil%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20year.%20That%20night%2C%20when%20she%20went%20out%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20friends%2C%20my%20mind%20wrestled%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20expectation%20and%20concern.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20my%20daughter%20went%20to%20college%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20let%20go%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKristil%20and%20I%20had%20always%20been%20close.%20I%20was%20not%20just%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mother-five-children-gave-up-bedroom-daughter-privacy-tiktok-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esingle%20mother%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20I%20was%20her%20only%20parent.%20We%20shared%20everything%2C%20a%20pattern%20that%20continued%20through%20her%20teenage%20years.%20When%20she%20entered%20high%20school%20and%20focused%20on%20academics%20with%20the%20dream%20of%20attending%20a%20top-rated%20college%2C%20I%20became%20her%20companion%20in%20supporting%20her%20to%20make%20that%20dream%20a%20reality.%20When%20she%20earned%20a%20full%20scholarship%20to%20an%20Ivy%20League%20college%2C%20I%20left%20her%20at%20the%20gates%20of%20Columbia%20University%20%E2%80%94%20a%20world%20away%20from%20our%20small%20Midwestern%20life%20in%20Wisconsin.%20It%20was%20a%20moment%20of%20both%20heartbreak%20and%20pride.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20her%20second%20year%20at%20Columbia%2C%20I%20noticed%20subtle%20changes%20in%20Kristil.%20When%20she%20returned%20home%20that%20Christmas%2C%20her%20language%2C%20style%2C%20and%20even%20her%20pace%20had%20shifted.%20She%20seemed%20to%20move%20through%20life%20with%20a%20new%2C%20brisk%20confidence.%20But%20our%20conversations%2C%20once%20filled%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilestone-birthday-trips-with-sisters-mom-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efamilial%20warmth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20began%20to%20feel%20more%20like%20intellectual%20exchanges.%20She%20questioned%20things%20more%2C%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20critical%20thinking%20skills%20she%20was%20developing%20in%20college.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20changes%20in%20our%20relationship%20dynamic.%20Discussions%20that%20used%20to%20be%20harmonious%20and%20agreeable%20became%20strained%20and%20challenging.%20Kristil%20questioned%20not%20just%20ideas%20and%20concepts%20but%20also%20beliefs%20and%20values%20that%20I%20thought%20we%20both%20had%20always%20agreed%20upon.%20These%20changes%20sometimes%20left%20me%20feeling%20uneasy%2C%20as%20if%20our%20shared%20perspectives%20were%20shifting%20beneath%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20response%20to%20this%20shift%20wasn't%20always%20ideal.%20I%20struggled%20to%20adjust%20to%20this%20new%20aspect%20of%20our%20relationship.%20I%20missed%20the%20simpler%20times%20when%20we%20used%20to%20talk%20more%20straightforwardly%20and%20were%20more%20aligned.%20Sadly%2C%20I%20started%20keeping%20things%20to%20myself%20and%20tip-toeing%20around%20issues%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20say%20something.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20confrontation%20with%20Kristil%20an