d%20with%20memories%20of%20her%20as%20a%20little%20girl%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20the%20change%20needed%20to%20come%20from%20within%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20night%2C%20I%20expressed%20all%20my%20emotions%20and%20feelings%2C%20clarifying%20that%20my%20apprehensions%20and%20anxieties%20were%20based%20on%20a%20profound%20and%20unwavering%20love%20for%20her.%20This%20love%20was%20unconditional%20and%20long-lasting.%20Though%20neither%20of%20us%20possessed%20all%20the%20solutions%2C%20we%20mutually%20agreed%20that%20searching%20for%20them%20was%20a%20journey%20worth%20embarking%20on.%20As%20we%20talked%20about%20setting%20boundaries%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20time%20together%2C%20we%20turned%20a%20new%20page%2C%20leaving%20our%20disagreement%20in%20the%20past.%20The%20rest%20of%20our%20visit%20was%20filled%20with%20the%20warmth%20of%20Christmas%20and%20conversations%20about%20our%20aspirations%20for%20the%20upcoming%20year%2C%20moments%20that%20we%20both%20cherished.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20weeks%20later%2C%20as%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20gazing%20out%20at%20the%20clouds%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20complex%20mix%20of%20emotions.%20My%20heart%20was%20heavy%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20loss%2C%20yet%20I%20was%20also%20feeling%20hopeful.%20Kristil%2C%20who%20had%20once%20depended%20on%20me%20for%20almost%20everything%2C%20was%20now%20navigating%20life%20on%20her%20terms.%20Our%20bond%20remained%20transformed%2C%20but%20intact.%20She%20still%20needed%20me%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20in%20a%20new%20way.%20As%20I%20considered%20our%20future%2C%20it%20became%20apparent%20that%20our%20journey%20together%20was%20simply%20unfolding%2C%20much%20like%20ourselves%2C%20into%20a%20new%20chapter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-bittersweet-changing-dynamic-with-daughter-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publi