nd%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20alert%20was%20sounded%20after%20inputs%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20about%20a%20suspected%20security%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20police%20has%20deputed%20about%2012%2C000%20personnel%20in%20and%20around%20Ayodhya%20after%20the%20fresh%20threats.%20They%20have%20also%20roped%20in%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20monitor%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMHA%20has%20sent%20a%20high-level%20cyber%20expert%20team%20to%20Ayodhya%20to%20deal%20with%20cyber%20threat%20before%20Pran%20Pratistha%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20level%20official%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20mega%20event%20and%20continuous%20inputs%20regarding%20misuse%20of%20cyberspace%20are%20being%20evaluated%20and%20alerts%20are%20being%20issued%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stated%20that%20integrated%20control%20rooms%20have%20been%20set%20up%20where%20threats%20are%20being%20monitored%20by%20various%20agencies%20on%20a%20real-time%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20that%20security%20agencies%20will%20use%20AI%20surveillance%20systems%20to%20identify%20suspicious%20activities%20and%20track%20down%20miscreants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20installed%20about%2010%2C000%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20and%20around%20Ayodhya%20city.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%20about%20400%20are%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20shrine%20and%20in%20the%20yellow%20zone.%20The%20yellow%20zone%20is%20where%20we%20are%20using%20AI%20for%20facial%20recognition%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Prashant%20Kumar%2C%20Director%20General%2C%20of%20Law%20and%20Order%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh's%20criminal%20database%20is%20being%20uploaded%20on%20the%20portals%20to%20assist%20AI%20in%20identifying%20and%20matching%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI-based%20CCTV%20surveillance%20system%20will%20also%20help%20in%20detecting%20frequent%20visitors%20or%20any%20common%20trend%20followed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20people%20while%20visiting%20the%20temple%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20and%20several%20other%20dignitaries%20will%20be%20attending%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rituals%20for%20the%20temple%20consecration%20started%20on%20January%2012.%20On%20January%2022%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20perform%20the%20puja%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BPran%20Pratistha'%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20A%20team%20of%20priests%20led%20by%20Lakshmikant%20Dixit%20will%20perform%20the%20main%20rituals%20of%20the%20Pran%20Prathistha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705660200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Flffau5b4_ayodhya-generic-streets-_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-how-ai-will-help-maintain-order-identify-rule-breakers-at-ayodhya-event-4892352%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20security%20levels%20in%20Ayodhya%20have%20been%20raised%20ahead%20of%20the%20grand%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20alert%20was%20sounded%20after%20inputs%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20about%20a%20suspected%20security%20breach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-how-ai-will-help-maintain-order-identify-rule-breakers-at-ayodhya-event-4892352%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-how-ai-will-help-maintain-order-identify-rule-breakers-at-ayodhya-event-4892352%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22