%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMarket%20overview%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFutures%20on%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20climbed%200.3%25%20to%204%2C825%20points%20as%20of%204%3A55%20a.m.%20ET%2C%20while%20similar%20contracts%20on%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20gained%200.6%25%20to%2017%2C207.75.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEuropean%20stocks%20remained%20in%20the%20green%2C%20with%20the%20Euro%20Stoxx%2050%20rising%200.3%25.%20Germany's%20DAX%2040%20index%20was%200.2%25%20higher%20and%20France's%20CAC%2040%20edged%20up%200.1%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrends%20were%20more%20mixed%20across%20Asian%20markets.%20Hong%20Kong's%20Hang%20Seng%20index%20and%20the%20Shanghai%20Composite%20fell%200.5%25%20each%2C%20but%20Japan's%20Nikkei%20225%20rallied%201.4%25%20to%2035%2C963.30.%20India's%20Nifty%2050%20rose%200.7%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20crypto%20market%2C%20bitcoin%20was%20at%20%2441%2C341%2C%20trading%20in%20a%20tight%20range%20after%20Thursday's%203.4%25%20sell-off.%20Ether%20was%20a%20tad%20higher%20at%20%242%2C478.50.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Dollar%20Index%2C%20which%20tracks%20the%20greenback%20against%20a%20basket%20of%20currencies%2C%20was%20stable%20near%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20more%20than%20a%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETen-year%20Treasury%20yields%20edged%20higher%20to%204.14%25.%20Brent%20crude%20oil%20rose%200.7%25%20to%20%2479.63%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-us-futures-advance-chipmakers-oil-rises-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705660004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c8018ec62ab5daf7f07ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-today-us-futures-advance-chipmakers-oil-rises-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20equity%20futures%20were%20on%20a%20strong%20footing%20Friday%2C%20with%20chipmakers%20from%20Texas%20Instruments%20to%20AMD%20and%20Nvidia%20leading%20premarket%20gains%20on%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22avarma%40insider.com%20(Anil%20Varma)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-today-us-futures-advance-chipmakers-oil-rises-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Ayodhya%20-%20Congress's%20Epic%20Tragedy%20Of%20Errors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOblivious%20of%20Congress's%20history%20and%20the%20part%20played%20by%20it%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20both%20obtrusively%20and%20unobtrusively%2C%20the%20current%20leadership%20of%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20has%20withdrawn%20into%20a%20self-glorifying%20cocoon%20and%20has%20decided%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20Monday%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20%26quot%3BModi's%20function%26quot%3B%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20put%20estoppels%20on%20the%20party.%20On%20January%2015%2C%20a%20motley%20group%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20took%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20river%20Sarayu%20in%20Ayodhya%20to%20mark%20Makar%20Sankranti.%20Ram%20ki%20Paidi%2C%20the%20series%20of%20ghats%20where%20the%20event%20took%20place%2C%20was%20refurbished%20to%20its%20present%20glory%20by%20the%20Congress%20regime%20of%20Sripati%20Misra%20in%201983%20after%20floods%20devastated%20Ayodhya.%20The%20then%20irrigation%20minister%2C%20Virbahadur%20Singh%20(who%20later%20became%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh)%2C%20played%20a%20yeoman%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20taking%20office%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20who%2C%20like%20Virbahadur%2C%20is%20from%20Gorakhpur%2C%20has%20used%20the%20Ram%20ki%20Paidi%20to%20enter%20the%20Guinness%20Book%20of%20records%20by%20lighting%20five%20lakh%20lamps%20on%20Diwali%20on%20its%20majestic%20ghats%20(the%20spectacle%20will%20be%20bettered%20on%20January%2022).%20The%20Congress%20leaders%20taking%20the%20ritualistic%20bath%20on%20Makar%20Sankranti%20were%20perhaps%20unaware%20of%20the%20role%20their%20party%20had%20played%20in%20providing%20this%20facility%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20is%20emerging%20as%20the%20'Hindu%20Vatican'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20alliance%20parties%20have%20echoed%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20sentiment%20and%20said%20they%20will%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20All%2C%20however%2C%20have%20created%20alibis.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20she%20will%20pray%20at%20Kalighat%20temple%20and%20lead%20a%20%26quot%3BHarmony%20rally'%20in%20Kolkata.%20Uddhav%20Thackrey%20is%20headed%20for%20Kalaram%20Temple%20in%20Nashik%2C%20from%20where%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20week%20began%20his%2011-day%20choreography%20of%20faith%2C%20of%20observing%20yam-niyam%20fasting%20and%20rituals%20to%20prepare%20himself%20for%20the%20Ayodhya%20ceremony.%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20have%20said%20they%20will%20visit%20Ayodhya%20on%20a%20later%20date.%20Kejriwal%20has%20started%20mass%20recitation%20of%20the%20Hanuman%20Chalisa%20in%20Delhi%2C%20organised%20by%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreceding%20the%20mega%20event%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Odisha's%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20who%20retains%20equidistance%20from%20all%20camps%2C%20has%20inaugurated%20a%20grand%20parikrama%20of%20the%20Jagannath%20temple%20at%20Puri.%20The%20revamp%20of%20temples%20is%20not%20confined%20to%20Puri%20alone.%20In%20Kolkata%2C%20the%20Kalighat%20temple%20is%20being%20refurbished.%20Vindhyavasini%20temple%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Mirzapur%20area%20is%20undergoing%20beautification.%20The%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20corridor%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20the%20ornamentalisation%20of%20Mahakal%20in%20Ujjain%20preceded%20these%20endeavours.%20Karnataka%20is%20planning%20a%20temple%20at%20Hampi%2C%20which%20is%20said%20to%20be%20Kishkindha%2C%20the%20legendary%20birthplace%20of%20Hanuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20ambivalent%20about%20what%20it%20plans%20to%20do%20on%20a%20day%20slated%20to%20be%20modern%20India's%20national%20carnival.%20(Speculation%20is%20that%20Rahul%20may%20visit%20the%20Kamakhya%20shrine%20in%20Guwahati.)%20After%20invites%20for%20the%20Pranpratishta%20ceremony%20were%20sent%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20party%20dithered%20for%20a%20fortnight%20before%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20announced%20that%20the%20three%20will%20stay%20away.%20The%20party's%20penchant%20for%20differing%20was%20marked%20by%20its%20usual%20dithering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murmur%20of%20dissent%20shrouds%20Congresspersons.%20Arjun%20Modhvadia%2C%20the%20party's%20MLA%20from%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20birthplace%20Porbandar%2C%20and%20Nirmal%20Khatri%2C%20ex-MLA%20from%20Faizabad%20(now%20Ayodhya)%2C%20have%20differed%20and%20sought%20course%20correction.%20Modhvadia%20and%20Khatri%20headed%20the%20Congress%20units%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20UP%20in%20the%20past.%20Himachal's%20Congress%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Sukhu%2C%20who%20had%20defied%20his%20party's%20diktat%20and%20attended%20PM%20Modi's%20G20%20dinner%2C%20declared%20on%20January%209%20his%20intention%20to%20be%20in%20Ayodhya.%20His%20ministerial%20colleague%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20too%20has%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20be%20in%20Ayodhya%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20respect%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20late%20father%20%26quot%3Bwho%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20Ram%20Jannmabhoomi%20movement%26quot%3B.%20(His%20father%2C%20Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20was%20a%20Congress%20stalwart.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20assassin%20Beant%20Singh%20not%20silenced%20Indira%20Gandhi%20on%2031%20October%201984%2C%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20may%20have%20had%20a%20chapter%2C%20which%20was%20nixed%20by%20bullets.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20scheduled%20to%20receive%20a%20delegation%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20to%20hear%20them%20on%20the%20Ayodhya%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VHP's%20Ram-Janaki%20Yatra%2C%20starting%20from%20Sita's%20birthplace%20Sitamarhi%20in%20Bihar%2C%20had%20travelled%20through%20Ayodhya%20and%20reached%20Delhi%20to%20highlight%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20issue.%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Congress%20Chief%20Minister%20Narayan%20Dutt%20Tiwari%20provided%20the%20VHP%20logistical%20support%20by%20assigning%20a%20medical%20team%20for%20the%20yatris.%20A%20memorandum%20was%20to%20be%20received%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%20on%20November%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yatra%20followed%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20VHP's%20first%20%26quot%3BDharma%20Sansad%26quot%3B%2C%20held%20earlier%20that%20year%20to%20consolidate%20Hindu%20preachers%20under%20an%20umbrella%20organisation.%20The%20meet%20was%20held%20in%20Delhi's%20Vigyan%20Bhavan.%20A%20year%20before%2C%20it%20had%20been%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20Non-Aligned%20Meet%2C%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi-era%20equivalent%20of%20Narendra%20Modi's%20G20%20triumph.%20Booking%20Vigyan%20Bhavan%20requires%20the%20government's%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201981%2C%20the%20conversion%20of%20some%201%2C100%20Dalits%20into%20Islam%20at%20Meenakshipuram%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Tirunelveli%20district%20raised%20a%20windstorm.%20Speaking%20in%20parliament%2C%20then%20Home%20Minister%20Gyani%20Zail%20Singh%20said%20conversions%20were%20%26quot%3Ba%20conspiracy%20of%20political%20motivation%26quot%3B.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20said%20to%20be%20unhappy.%20(All%201%2C100%20returned%20to%20the%20Hindu%20fold%20after%20'shuddhikaran'%20by%20VHP.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VHP%2C%20founded%20in%201964%2C%20had%20been%20somewhat%20dormant%20at%20the%20time.%20Meenakshipuram%20triggered%20its%20reactivation.%20Covert%20consultations%20ensued%20between%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20and%20then%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20Sarsanghchalak%2C%20Balasaheb%20Deoras%20(whose%20brother%20Bhaurao%2C%20a%20leading%20RSS%20ideologue%2C%20acted%20as%20conduit).%20The%20RSS%20and%20Congress%20had%20engaged%20in%20low-key%20dialogue%20since%20the%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20days.%20They%20reached%20a%20crescendo%20in%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeenakshipuram%20saw%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Virat%20Hindu%20Parishad%20under%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Vedic%20scholar%20Dr%20Karan%20Singh.%20The%20group%20had%20taken%20out%20a%20nationwide%20Ekatmata%20Yatra.%20Dr%20Singh%2C%20now%2092%2C%20has%20criticised%20his%20party's%20January%2022%2C%202024%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20launched%20in%20April%201982%20by%20former%20Jan%20Sangh%20members%20who%20broke%20away%20from%20the%20Janata%20Party%20(into%20which%20the%201951-founded%20Jana%20Sangh%20had%20merged%20in%201977).%20The%20nascent%20party%20won%20only%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20post-Indira%20Gandhi%20polls%20of%20December%201984.%20Meenakshipuram%20and%20later%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20emerged%20as%20the%20BJP's%20clarion%20call%20over%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201989%2C%20the%20Congress%20dwindled%20from%20404%20to%20197%20while%20the%20BJP%20increased%20its%20strength%2043%20times%20to%20reach%2087%20till%20then%20the%20highest%20tally%20of%20a%20Sangh%20outfit%20ever.%20In%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20the%20Congress%20shrank%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20bolstered%20by%20its%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20stand%2C%20grew%20from%20strength%20to%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201986%20decision%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20to%20reverse%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20in%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20case%2C%20under%20pressure%20from%20conservative%20Muslims%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20move%20in%20which%20the%20Sharia%20law%20was%20given%20precedence%20over%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20This%20sharpened%20the%20Ayodhya%20demand.%20The%20BJP%20added%20Ayodhya%20to%20its%20core%20agenda%20through%20the%20Palampur%20resolution%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20balance%20the%20feelings%20of%20both%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20agreed%20to%20open%20the%20lock%20at%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20site%20in%20Ayodhya%20(the%20keys%20could%20not%20be%20found%3B%20the%20locks%20were%20broken%20open%20by%20the%20government%20under%20a%20magistrate's%20order).%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%201989%20elections%2C%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20allowed%20the%20shilanyas%20(foundation%20stone%20laying)%20of%20the%20temple%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20began%20the%201989%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%20at%20Ayodhya%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20%26quot%3BRam%20Rajya%26quot%3B.%20In%201991%2C%20the%20Congress%20promised%20a%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20its%20poll%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20telecast%20of%20Ramanand%20Sagar's%20Ramayan%20serial%20on%20Doordarshan%20(the%20only%20TV%20channel%20then)%20since%201987%20had%20been%20initially%20opposed%20by%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20HKL%20Bhagat.%20A%20letter%20from%20Balasaheb%20Deoras%2C%20which%20addressed%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20as%20%26quot%3BCheeranjiv%20Rajiv%26quot%3B%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20clinched%20the%20issue.%20The%20Ramayan%20serial%20played%20a%20yeoman%20role%20in%20build%20up%20to%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20fervour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20banishment%20of%20the%20Congress%20as%20the%20dominant%20political%20party%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20party%20of%20governance%20ensued%20post%201989.%20A%20headline%20in%20the%20Times%20of%20India%20on%2010%20November%202019%2C%20post%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BRajiv%20opened%20the%20lock%3B%20saffron%20got%20the%20key%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyodhya%20has%20been%20a%20saga%20of%20the%20Congress's%20tragedy%20of%20errors.%20Staying%20away%20from%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20carnival%20will%20add%20yet%20another%20chapter%20to%20this%20epic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705659540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8q8drbf4_rahul-gandhi-1200-_625x300_19_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fayodhya-congresss-epic-tragedy-of-errors-4892422%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oblivious%20of%20Congress's%20history%20and%20the%20part%20played%20by%20it%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20both%20obtrusively%20and%20unobtrusively%2C%20the%20current%20leadership%20of%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20has%20withdrawn%20into%20a%20self-glorifying%20cocoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fayodhya-congresss-epic-tragedy-of-errors-4892422%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fayodhya-congresss-epic-tragedy-of-errors-4892422%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fayodhya-congresss-epic-tragedy-of-errors-4892422%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shahid%20Kapoor%20will%20do%20THIS%20if%20he%20gets%20magic%20lamp%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705659151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106987103%2Cimgsize-43248.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshahid-kapoor-will-do-this-if-he-gets-alauddin-lamp-for-a-day%2Farticleshow%2F106987103.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F