ity%20they%20expect%20is%20a%20top%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Walmart%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BPerishable%20items%20must%20be%20delivered%20within%20a%20certain%20time%20period%2C%20which%20begins%20when%20the%20first%20perishable%20item%20is%20shopped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20instances%20when%20an%20order%20is%20not%20delivered%20within%20the%20designated%20time%20period%2C%C2%A0drivers%20are%20asked%20to%20return%20the%20order%20to%20the%20store%2C%20and%20we%20give%20customers%20the%20option%20for%20redelivery%20or%20a%20refund%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20after%20he%20posted%20his%20initial%20video%2C%20Aaron%20told%20BI%20that%20most%20of%20the%20workers%20he%20filmed%20were%20gone%20and%20had%20been%20replaced%20with%20others%20who%20followed%20the%20same%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221899%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shopping%20carts%20with%20groceries%20in%20a%20Walmart%20parking%20lot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a9454143bb77284b9e137c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221069%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20car%20arrived%2C%20but%20the%20individuals%20didn't%20load%20the%20groceries%20into%20it%2C%20instead%20waiting%20for%20another%20vehicle.%3Cp%3EUber%20Lyft%20Phoenix%20on%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn-store%20shopping%20orders%20tended%20to%20pay%20better%20than%20curbside-pickup%20orders%2C%20Aaron%20said%2C%20and%20while%20he%20once%20had%20a%20reliable%20mix%20of%20the%20two%2C%20it%20had%20been%20about%20two%20weeks%20since%20his%20last%20shop%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20wasn't%20only%20frustrated%20with%20seeing%20people%20snag%20the%20best%20shopping%20orders%20without%20a%20car%20to%20deliver%20them%20in%2C%20but%20also%20with%20the%20way%20they%20were%20handling%20customers'%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWalmart%20has%20time%20limits%20on%20deliver