20ongoing%20T20I%20series%20against%20Kiwis%2C%20Pakistan%20are%20trailing%203-0%2C%20with%20two%20games%20to%20go.%20In%20the%20series%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20opening%20with%20new%20openers%2C%20Saim%20Ayub%20and%20Mohammed%20Rizwan%2C%20who%20have%20underperformed%20as%20a%20pair%20in%20this%20series%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20YouTube%20Channel%2C%20Raja%20voiced%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20much%20pressure%20was%20created%20to%20break%20the%20opening%20pair%20of%20Babar%20and%20Rizwan.%20After%20breaking%20the%20opening%20partnership%2C%20which%20was%20evaluated%20based%20on%20the%20strike%20rate.%20When%20you%20bring%20in%20new%20players%2C%20they%20may%20perform%20well%20in%20leagues%2C%20but%20international%20cricket%20is%20a%20different%20beast%20where%20there%20is%20pressure%2C%20and%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20on%20you.%20You%20broke%20the%20opening%20pair%20that%20was%20famous%20worldwide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20you%20have%20a%20workshop%20of%20trained%20openers%20behind%20you%20who%20are%20gradually%20being%20introduced%2C%20when%20you%20have%20no%20other%20options.%20It%20takes%20time%20to%20form%20an%20opening%20pair.%20It%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20task.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20pair%2C%20and%20they%20consistently%20kept%20you%20in%20the%20field%20during%20matches%2C%20what%20benefit%20did%20you%20get%20after%20breaking%20it%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20he%20backs%20every%20skipper%2C%20including%20the%20current%20T20I%20skipper%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accusation%20made%20against%20me%20was%20that%20I%20backed%20Babar%20Azam.%20I%20support%20every%20captain%20because%20their%20role%20is%20to%20lead%20not%20just%20on%20the%20field%20during%20the%20game%2C%20but%20also%20extends%20to%20off%20the%20field%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20Raja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizwan%20and%20Babar%20have%20the%20h