%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20in%20Khavda.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9ku0q564_adani-solar-plant_625x300_19_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20installing%20solar%20panels%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20in%20Khavda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country%20and%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy%20needs%20ever%20more%20power%2C%20and%20Adani%20is%20building%20what%20he%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bmonumental%26quot%3B%20solar%20and%20wind%20project%20he%20boasts%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bvisible%20even%20from%20space%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20wind%20whips%20up%20sand%20in%20the%20baking%20heat%20of%20the%20Rann%20of%20Kutch%20desert%2C%20thousands%20of%20labourers%20erect%20vast%20rows%20of%20solar%20panels%2C%20dig%20foundations%20for%20wind%20turbines%20and%20lay%20seemingly%20endless%20rolls%20of%20wires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESagar%20Adani%2C%20Gautam's%20nephew%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%2C%20told%20AFP%20that%20the%20project's%20teams%20are%20working%20%26quot%3Bat%20an%20accelerated%20pace%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20complete%20in%202027%2C%20the%20%242.3-billion%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20will%20cover%20726%20square%20kilometres%20(280%20square%20miles)%20--%20nearly%20the%20size%20of%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20park%20is%20aimed%20to%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20generate%2030%20gigawatts%20of%20solar%20and%20wind%20energy%20--%20enough%20to%20power%20the%20homes%20of%2018%20million%20people%2C%20more%20than%20the%20combined%20populations%20of%20London%20and%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20will%20produce%2017GW%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20generated%20by%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Workers%20operating%20a%20machine%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20solar%20panel%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20in%20Khavda.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%20Workers%20operating%20a%20machine%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20solar%20panel%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20in%20Khavda.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdm3qqhj8_adani-solar-plant_625x300_19_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20operating%20a%20machine%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20solar%20panel%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20in%20Khavda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20slated%20to%20produce%20a%20third%20more%20power%20than%20China's%20Three%20Gorges%20Dam%2C%20currently%20the%20world's%20biggest%20power-generating%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Proud%20Indian'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20is%20the%20showpiece%20of%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20--%20in%20which%20France's%20TotalEnergies%20bought%20a%2019.7%20percent%20stake%20for%20%242.5%20billion%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mundra%2C%20site%20of%20India's%20largest%20commercial%20port%20--%20run%20by%20another%20arm%20of%20the%20Adani%20empire%20--%20it%20is%20manufacturing%20key%20components%20for%20its%20aggressive%20solar%20and%20wind%20energy%20foray%2C%20including%20colossal%20wind%20turbine%20blades%20nearly%2080%20metres%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolar%20panels%20are%20churned%20out%20on%20high-tech%20production%20lines%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20creating%20one%20of%20the%20globe's%20most%20extensive%20and%20integrated%20renewable%20energy%20manufacturing%20ecosystems%20for%20solar%20and%20wind%2C%26quot%3B%20Adani%20wrote%20last%20month%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20where%20he%20describes%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BProud%20Indian.%20Excited%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20India%20growth%20story!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20has%20called%20for%20ambitious%20clean%20energy%20projects%20to%20create%20500%20gigawatts%20of%20renewable%20capacity%20to%20meet%20half%20its%20energy%20needs%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20--%20who%20rejected%20Hindenburg's%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Bmaliciously%20mischievous%26quot%3B%20--%20has%20said%20he%20will%20invest%20an%20estimated%20%24100%20billion%20into%20that%20energy%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20fully%20operational%2C%20Adani's%20renewable%20energy%20park%20will%20make%20up%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20quarter%20of%20India's%20current%20capacity%20from%20wind%20and%20solar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Employees%20working%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20wind%20turbine%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%20Employees%20working%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20wind%20turbine%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fapa8rphc_adani-wind-plant_625x300_19_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployees%20working%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20wind%20turbine%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20owned%20Khavda%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20India%20also%20plans%20to%20sharply%20increase%20its%20coal-based%20power%20capacity%20and%20vows%20to%20become%20carbon%20neutral%20only%20by%202070%2C%20two%20decades%20later%20than%20many%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Mirrors%20India's%20ambitions'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Malik%2C%20from%20the%20Asia%20Group%20consultancy%2C%20said%20the%20Adani%20Group%20is%20%26quot%3Bsitting%20on%20very%20solid%20assets%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmirrors%20India's%20ambitions%20and%20hopes%20and%20strategy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20said%20Adani%2C%20like%20all%20of%20India's%20conglomerates%20and%20major%20multinationals%20in%20the%20country%2C%20were%20%26quot%3Bbroadly%20aligning%26quot%3B%20themselves%20with%20the%20government's%20economic%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20perfect%20sense%20for%20a%20company%20which%20is%20solely%20invested%20in%20India's%20energy%20sector%20to%20start%20looking%20at%20clean%20and%20renewable%20energy%20to%20shift%20from%20coal%20--%20though%20coal%20will%20not%20entirely%20go%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Malik%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20energy%20park%2C%20workers%20in%20hard%20hats%20and%20neon%20jackets%20wrap%20their%20faces%20in%20cloth%20for%20protection%20from%20the%20biting%20sand%20and%20blazing%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20manager%2C%20who%20was%20not%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media%2C%20said%20the%20conditions%20were%20%26quot%3Bchallenging%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20construction%20was%20%26quot%3Bawe-inspiring%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20is%20around%2075%20kilometres%20from%20the%20nearest%20village%2C%20and%20about%20six%20kilometres%20from%20the%20heavily%20militarised%20border%20with%20nuclear-armed%20arch-rival%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20grand%20projects%20often%20come%20at%20a%20heavy%20environmental%20footprint%2C%20but%20local%20conservationist%20Mahendra%20Bhanani%20said%20that%20while%20he%20would%20like%20a%20study%20on%20its%20impacts%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%20the%20energy%20park%20is%20far%20from%20human%20settlements%20and%20biodiversity%20hotspots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSolar%20energy%20is%20better%20than%20many%20polluting%20chemical%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Med