%20and%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20were%20in%20a%20relationship%20for%20seven%20years%20before%20breaking%20up%20in%202016.%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%20in%C2%A0June%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20led%20to%20Ankita's%20mother%2C%20Vandana%20Lokhande%20and%20Vicky's%20mother%2C%20Ranjana%20Jain%2C%20also%20speaking%20about%20the%20late%20actor.%20The%20Internet%20has%20been%20largely%20divided%20on%20Ankita's%20choice%20to%20talk%20about%20her%20past%20relationship%20while%20on%20the%20show%20with%20her%20husband.%20While%20one%20section%20deems%20it%20her%20right%20to%20speak%20about%20all%20aspects%20of%20her%20life%2C%20several%20viewers%20have%20accused%20Ankita%20of%20using%20Sushant's%20anecdotes%20for%20sympathy%2C%20a%20belief%20shared%20by%20Vicky's%20mother%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20what%20Ankita%20Lokhande%2C%20Vicky%20Jain%20and%20their%20family%20members%C2%A0have%20said%20about%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20on%20%3Cem%3EBigg%20Boss%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnkita%20Lokhande%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkita%20Lokhande%20has%20been%20quite%20vocal%20about%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbigg-boss-17-ankita-lokhande-on-her-break-up-with-sushant-singh-rajput-4530764%5C%22%3Erelationship%20and%20subsequent%20breakup%20with%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Speaking%20to%20fellow%20contestant%20Munawar%20about%20their%20breakup%2C%20she%20said%20early%20in%20the%20show%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20reason%20%5Bfor%20the%20breakup%5D.%20And%20I%20was%20blank.%20%3Cem%3EEk%20raat%20main%20cheezay%20palti%20hain.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWoh%20%5BSushant%20Singh%20Rajput%5D%20ek%20dum%20ek%20raat%20mein%20gayab%20ho%20gaya.%20Success%20mil%20rahi%20thi%20toh%20log%20uske%20kaan%20bhar%20rahe%20the.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EMainay%20usko