ithholds%20Funds%20From%20Bengal%20for%20Not%20Displaying%20PM%20Photo%20at%20Ration%20Shops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19122302%2FUntitled-design-7.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20an%20absurd%20attempt%20to%20coerce%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20publicity%20campaign%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20withheld%20Rs%207%2C000%20crore%20from%20the%20state%20for%20not%20displaying%20his%20photos%20at%20ration%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20directive%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FJan%2F19%2Fwest-bengal-no-signboards-with-pm-pix-at-ration-shops-central-government-holds-release-of-funds%5C%22%3E%20display%20sign%20boards%20and%20flexes%3C%2Fa%3E%20featuring%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA)%20logo%20and%20photos%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20ration%20shops%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20being%20withheld%20from%20the%20state%20was%20to%20procure%20paddy%20for%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20schemes.%20State%20government%20officials%20said%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20reimburse%20the%20sum%20could%20leave%20a%20serious%20impact%20on%20paddy%20collection%20on%20the%20state%20in%20the%20ongoing%20financial%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FJan%2F19%2Fwest-bengal-no-signboards-with-pm-pix-at-ration-shops-central-government-holds-release-of-funds%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20has%20already%20procured%208.52%20lakh%20tonnes%20for%20the%20NFSA%20schemes%20in%20this%20financial%20year%20for%20the%20central%20pool.%20It%20has%20procured%2022%20lakh%20tonnes%20of%20paddy%2C%20including%20the%20volume%20for%20the%20central%20pool%2C%20against%20its%20annual%20target%20of%2070%20lakh%20tonnes%20this%20year.%20But%20the%20state%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20reimbursed%20for%20the%20paddy%20it%20procured%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20state%20government%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FJan%2F19%2Fwest-bengal-no-signboards-with-pm-pix-at-ration-shops-central-government-holds-release-of-funds%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20state%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%20procuring%2080%25%20of%20its%20annual%20goal%20of%2070%20lakh%20tonnes%20during%20this%20season%2C%20which%20continues%20until%20February-end.%20If%20the%20state%20does%20not%20receive%20sufficient%20funds%20within%20this%20window%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FJan%2F19%2Fwest-bengal-no-signboards-with-pm-pix-at-ration-shops-central-government-holds-release-of-funds%5C%22%3Ethe%20entire%20procurement%20process%20could%20be%20adversely%20affected.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20the%20first%20tussle%20over%20branding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20withheld%20funds%20from%20West%20Bengal%20over%20branding%20issues.%20In%20November%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmamata-writes-to-modi-urging-release-of-funds%2Farticle67591835.ece%5C%22%3EBanerjee%20had%20written%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20urging%20him%20to%20release%20funds%20under%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20(NHM)%20that%20were%20withheld%20due%20to%20the%20colour%20of%20the%20health%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20earnestly%20request%20you%20to%20kindly%20inte