%20different%20firing%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2017%2C%20a%20gunfight%20between%20militant%20groups%20and%20security%20forces%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20one%20Indian%20Reserve%20Battalion%20(IRB)%20jawan%20and%20one%20Manipur%20Rifles%20jawan.%20This%20incident%20triggered%20a%20significant%20protest%20in%20Imphal%2C%20led%20by%20women%20who%20demanded%20the%20resignation%20of%20Kuldiep%20Singh%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Unified%20Command%20of%20State%20and%20central%20forces%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20Coordination%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%20echoed%20the%20same%20demand%2C%20expressing%20concerns%20about%20the%20breakdown%20of%20security%20arrangements%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20escalated%20when%20a%20mob%20attempted%20to%20breach%20the%20Thoubal%20Police%20Headquarters%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Thoubal%2C%20and%20the%20security%20forces%20then%20employed%20force.%20Armed%20miscreants%20from%20the%20mob%20fired%20live%20rounds%2C%20resulting%20in%20injuries%20to%20three%20BSF%20personnel%3A%20Constable%20Gourav%20Kumar%2C%20ASI%20Sobram%20Singh%20and%20ASI%20Ramji.%20The%20injured%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20evacuated%20to%20Raj%20Medicity%20for%20medical%20treatment.%20There%20were%20also%20attempts%20to%20loot%20weapons%20from%20the%20police%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudents%20in%20Churachandpur%20on%20the%20streets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20complexity%2C%20students%20in%20Churachandpur%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20protest%20alleging%20educational%20biases%20imposed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government.%20Since%20May%203%2C%20tribals%20previously%20living%20in%20Imphal%20have%20faced%20challenges%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20universities%20in%20the%20Imphal%20Valley.%20While%20some%20were%20welcomed%20by%20universities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20those%20who%