%20with%20my%20mother%20passionately%20emphasising%20how%20diets%20in%20the%20past%20were%20enriched%20with%20superfoods%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20enough%2C%20millets%20are%20now%20being%20recognised%20as%20superfoods%20worldwide.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F137728%2Findian-government-ban-e-cigarettes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20government%20%3C%2Fa%3Edesignated%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CYear%20of%20Millets%E2%80%9D%20to%20underscore%20their%20numerous%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20challenge%20arises%20due%20to%20the%20limited%20availability%20of%20dedicated%20stores%20offering%20a%20variety%20of%20millets.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20fast-paced%20world%2C%20what%20most%20of%20us%20need%20is%20ready-to-use%20recipes%2C%20and%20not%20many%20producers%20offer%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20millet%20options.%20Recognising%20this%20gap%2C%20I%20founded%20my%20own%20millet%20startup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sai%20Krishna%20Popuri%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Health%20Sutra%2C%20as%20shared%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20behind%20a%20millet-based%20brand%2C%20offers%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20millet%20products%20through%20his%20startup.%20From%20Jowar%20Flakes%20to%20Millet%20Muesli%20and%20Millet%20Idli%20Rawa%20pre-mix%2C%20the%20brand%20aims%20to%20seamlessly%20integrate%20this%20superfood%20into%20your%20daily%20diet.%20With%20thousands%20of%20products%20sold%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20achieved%20an%20impressive%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98For%20a%20healthy%20and%20long%20life%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20engineering%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Sai%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20corporate%20job%20in%20the%20education%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20working%20a%20job%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20ventureship.%20I%20had%20always%20dreamt%20of%20being%20an%20entrepreneur.%20I%20was%20only%20waiting%20for%20the%20right%20idea%20to%20come%20along%20for%20me%20to%20take%20the%20leap%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20recalls%20that%20while%20he%20was%20in%20college%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20his%20own%20business%20and%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20ideas%20too.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20ideas%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20stood%20out%20and%20was%20benefitting%20the%20society%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20start%20a%20millet-based%20startup%20called%20Health%20Sutra.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20start%20a%20millet-based%20startup%20called%20Health%20Sutra.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20startups%20have%20always%20been%20an%20area%20of%20interest%20for%20Sai.%20%E2%80%9CFood%20tech%20has%20always%20been%20interesting%20to%20me.%20Before%20Health%20Sutra%2C%20I%20was%20working%20on%20an%20Indo-Chinese%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289275%2Fhyderabad-startup-banyan-nation-recycles-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-product-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20my%20father%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20diabetes.%20The%20doctor%20recommended%20various%20alternatives%20such%20as%20wheat%2C%20oats%2C%20or%20quinoa%20for%20his%20diet.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20wonder%20%E2%80%93%20oats%20are%20fine%2C%20but%20quinoa%20is%20imported%20from%20South%20America.%20Why%20opt%20for%20something%20from%20halfway%20across%20the%20world%20when%20we%20have%20equally%20good%20options%20right%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20find%20alternatives%20in%20India%2C%20he%20went%20looking%20for%20options.%20He%20met%20a%20relative%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20food%20science%20department%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20passionately%20discussing%20millets%20and%20how%20they%20are%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20next%20big%20thing.%20Millets%2C%20being%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20our%20land%2C%20boast%20indigenous%20qualities%2C%20robustness%2C%20and%20drought%20resistance%2C%20making%20them%20a%20highly%20beneficial%20choice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20research%2C%20Sai%20realised%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20superfood%20was%20not%20as%20popular%20as%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20processing%20technology%20for%20wheat%2C%20rice%2C%20and%20corn%20has%20advanced%20significantly.%20However%2C%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20millets.%20The%20limited%20progress%20in%20milling%20and%20further%20processing%20of%20millets%20creates%20a%20situation%20where%20presenting%20millets%20to%20consumers%20in%20a%20modern%20context%2C%20or%20offering%20them%20a%20contemporary%20perspective%20on%20their%20traditional%20foods%20and%20roots%2C%20becomes%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20change%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336185%2Fraimati-ghiuria-preserves-traditional-millets-at-her-odisha-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperspective%20towards%20millet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20make%20it%20more%20easily%20accessible%20to%20consumers%2C%20Sai%20started%20his%20research%20and%20development%20in%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20grandmas%20were%20right%20to%20ask%20us%20to%20include%20millets%20in%20our%20diets%20as%20they%20are%20traditionally%20considered%20to%20be%20healthy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202014%2C%20he%20was%20ready%20with%20his%20first%20product.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20launched%20jowar%20porridge%20under%20our%20brand%20Health%20Sutra%20and%20it%20got%20a%20great%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20company%20has%20experienced%20significant%20growth%2C%20introducing%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20products.%20These%20include%20cereal%20flakes%20such%20as%20Jowar%20Flakes%2C%20Ragi%20Flakes%2C%20and%20Barley%20Flakes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20different%20types%20of%20rava%20for%20idli%20and%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20biscuits%20made%20from%20ragi%20and%20jowar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGPq4_7FYhS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel