ndamentally%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20filterless%20air%20purification%20using%20cold%20plasma%20technology%20was%20possible%20and%20was%20alternatively%20also%20experimenting%20with%20bioengineering%20techniques%20for%20purifying%20air%20in%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20team%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20an%20office%20or%20access%20to%20capital%2C%20all%20experimenting%20of%20the%20core%20tech%20was%20done%20in%20public%20parking%20lots%20or%20park%20benches%20in%20Atlanta%20during%20after-hours%20or%20on%20weekends.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20Angad%20and%20his%20team%20of%20over%2030%20volunteers%20developed%20the%20first%20prototypes%20for%20filterless%20air%20purification%20devices%20and%20learned%20how%20to%20design%20test%20rigs%20for%20building%20these%20systems%20%E2%80%93%20a%20process%20they%20say%20they%20continue%20to%20invent%20and%20learn%20from%20even%20today%2C%206%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20the%20time%20when%20the%20project%20got%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Praan%E2%80%99.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20Angad%20and%20a%20few%20members%20of%20the%20team%20even%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20in%20India%20to%20propose%20a%20filterless%20approach%20to%20outdoor%20air%20purification.%20Following%20this%2C%20in%20December%202018%2C%20they%20flew%20to%20New%20Delhi%20and%20demonstrated%20the%20concept%20for%20their%20first%20prototype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSoon%20after%20this%2C%20the%20conversations%20around%20Praan%E2%80%99s%20mission%20grew%20within%20the%20Georgia%20Tech%20and%20Emory%20University%20Campuses%2C%20leading%20to%20many%20more%20people%20applying%20to%20join%20the%20team%20of%20volunteers%20working%20on%20this%20mission.%20In%20a%20fraction%20of%20weeks%2C%20the%20team%20grew%20to%2064%20people%20in%20the%20Spring%202019.%20This%20was%20the%20largest%20volunteering%20team%20%5Bthat%5D%20Praan%20ever%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20the%20Praan%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20develop%20filterless%20large%20space%20air%20purification%20technology%2C%20you%20need%20persons%20with%20different%20specialisations%E2%80%94mechanical%20designers%2C%20chemical%20engineers%2C%20physicists%2C%20full-stack%20developers%20and%20those%20with%20an%20understanding%20of%20power%20electronics%20and%20embedded%20hardware%2C%20among%20others.%20When%20I%20started%20developing%20this%20technology%20in%20my%20sophomore%20year%2C%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20build%20prototypes%20but%20knew%20nothing%20about%20fluid%20dynamics%2C%E2%80%9D%20Angad%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20lot%20of%20painstaking%20work%20into%20developing%20Praan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_354815808_1636878010145670_2433152274006099821_n_1080-1705505336-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338475%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20lot%20of%20painstaking%20work%20into%20developing%20Praan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20you%20entice%20student%20volunteers%20to%20work%20on%20your%20project%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20give%20them%20recognition%20on%20patents%2C%20which%20is%20very%20valuable%20for%20a%20third%20or%20fourth-year%20engineering%20student.%20And%20if%20you%20can%20give%20them%20real%20hands-on%20skills%2C%20which%20they%20are%20practising%20through%20that%20semester%2C%20they%20have%20a%20good%20story%20to%20tell%20to%20job%20recruiters.%20Plus%2C%20given%20my%20prior%20experience%20at%20MIT%20and%20the%20network%20I%20developed%20there%2C%20I%20knew%20senior%20people%20who%20worked%20in%20companies%20like%20Apple%2C%20Tesla%20or%20SpaceX.%20I%20could%20help%20introduce%20these%20volunteers%20to%20these%20people%2C%20saying%20they%20worked%20on%20my%20project.%20For%20example%2C%20Patrick%20Finley%2C%20the%20founder%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flanderchallenge.space%2Fteam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Lander%20Challenger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20went%20to%20work%20at%20SpaceX%20after%20working%20as%20a%20volunteer%20for%20Praan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20summer%2C%20Angad%20returned%20to%20India%20with%20one%20of%20his%20Teaching%20Assistants%20(TAs)%20and%20ran%20further%20experiments%20at%20a%20store%20room%20belonging%20to%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20company.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Naresh%20Shahani%20(currently%20a%20director%20at%20Praan)%2C%20helped%20obtain%20an%20unsecured%20loan%20of%20%2415%2C000%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20and%20development.%20Taken%20in%20Angad%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20this%20sum%20was%20eventually%20doubled%20and%20returned%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20summer%2C%20Angad%2C%20his%20TA%20and%20two%20interns%20put%20together%20the%20prototype%20of%20what%20would%20become%20the%20MKOne%20Outdoor%20Air%20Purifier.%20The%20plan%20moving%20forward%20was%20that%20Angad%20would%20graduate%20in%202020%2C%20run%20this%20company%20full-time%20after%20graduating%2C%20and%20raise%20capital.%20Despite%20his%20best%20efforts%2C%20securing%20funding%20was%20a%20major%20challenge.%20By%20January%202020%2C%20investors%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20caught%20on%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20deep%20tech%20and%20the%20offers%20on%20the%20table%20were%20not%20satisfactory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20he%20managed%20%E2%80%9Cto%20pool%20together%20some%20soft%20commitments%20worth%20%241.35M%20from%20an%20Indian%20VC%20fund%20and%20a%20few%20strategic%20angels%20on%20very%20bad%20investment%20terms%E2%80%9D.%20As%20these%20deals%20were%20being%20finalised%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%20and%20everything%20fell%20apart.%20Yet%20to%20graduate%20from%20college%2C%20he%20had%20to%20pack%20everything%20up%20and%20come%20back%20to%20India%20while%20completing%20online%20classes%20to%20get%20his%20degree.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20a%20silver%20lining.%20Since%20people%20were%20losing%20their%20jobs%20and%20internships%2C%20there%20were%20many%20looking%20to%20work%20on%20something%20that%20would%20advance%20their%20careers.%20Similar%20to%20what%20he%20did%20earlier%2C%20Angad%20offered%20recognition%20on%20Praan%20patents%20to%20anyone%20who%20helped%20develop%20the%20technology%20further%20either%20remotely%20or%20even%20as%20a%20volunteer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20Praan%20managed%20to%20onboard%20about%2060%20volunteers%20from%20multiple%20time%20zones%20who%20chose%20to%20dedicate%20about%20four%20months%20of%20their%20time%20to%20work%20on%20their%20technology.%C2%A0%20While%20the%20hardware%20was%20built%20and%20developed%20out%20of%20Angad%20and%20his%20intern%E2%80%99s%20bedrooms%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337225%2Fvolunteer-beach-cleanup-akshat-shah-shubh-mehta-mumbai-new-year-resolution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20other%20volunteers%20from%20around%20the%20world%20contributed%20with%20their%20ideas%20and%20engineering%20drawings%20for%20their%20prototypes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Praan%20website%2C%20there%20were%20also%20%E2%80%9Cdesign%20teams%20working%20on%20ideas%20for%20the%20MK%20One%20product%2C%20the%20indoor%20air%20purification%2C%20bioengineering%2C%20carbon%20capture%2C%20and%20software%20engineering%20products%E2%80%94all%20without%20any%20capital%20in%20the%20bank%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal%20funding%20and%20assistance%20finally%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Emergent%20Ventures%2C%20a%20fellowship%20and%20grant%20programme%20run%20by%20famous%20economist%20Dr.%20Tyler%20Cowen.%20It%20gave%20this%20fledgling%20startup%20the%20largest%20grant%20during%20the%20lockdown%20period%20which%20helped%20them%20access%20capital%20to%20build%20prototypes%20and%20test%20rigs%20as%20well.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20they%20developed%20a%20working%20prototype%20of%20the%20MKOne%20Outdoor%20Air%20purifier%20in%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20very%20little%20customer%20or%20investor%20interest%20and%20a%20negligible%20amount%20of%20vendors%20were%20willing%20to%20manufacture%20the%20MKOne%20prototype.%20Angad%20spent%20about%20five%20months%20waiting%20for%20vendors%20to%20manufacture%20the%20first%20usable%20MKOne%20prototype.%20Tired%20of%20waiting%2C%20Angad%20decided%20%E2%80%9Cto%20build%20the%20first%20MKOne%20prototype%20at%20a%20utensil%20manufacturing%20plant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C