20he%20volunteered%20to%20join%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F166365%2Fbhopal-cop-best-cyber-cop-award-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolice%20force%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20a%20COVID%20volunteer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20engineering%20background%2C%20I%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20cybersecurity.%20I%20had%20also%20worked%20with%20a%20cybersecurity%20company%20previously%2C%20so%20I%20had%20little%20knowledge%20of%20such%20matters.%20I%20also%20worked%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20cyber%20security%20volunteering%20force%20for%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20without%20a%20paid%20job%2C%20Murthy%20had%20already%20started%20exhausting%20his%20savings.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20when%20my%20friend%20informed%20me%20about%20an%20instant%20loan%20application%20and%20installed%20it%20on%20my%20phone.%20After%20he%20installed%20the%20app%2C%20I%20instantly%20received%20Rs%206%2C000.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20use%20the%20money%20as%20I%20found%20out%20that%20it%20was%20not%20affiliated%20with%20the%20RBI%20or%20any%20other%20banks.%20They%20were%20all%20loan%20sharks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyway%2C%20they%20told%20me%20that%20I%20would%20be%20charged%20at%20an%2018%20percent%20rate%20of%20interest%20per%20day%20and%20I%20have%20to%20return%20the%20entire%20amount%20within%20six%20days.%20In%20a%20few%20days%2C%20I%20was%20called%20again%2C%20but%20this%20time%20the%20person%20started%20abusing%20me%20using%20foul%20language.%20He%20also%20warned%20me%20that%20if%20I%20do%20not%20return%20the%20amount%2C%20he%20will%20share%20my%20morphed%20images%20to%20defame%20me.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20access%20to%20all%20my%20contacts%20and%20my%20gallery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201296px)%20100vw%2C%201296px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1-1705500219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murthy%20advises%20victims%20to%20report%20cyber%20complaints%20at%20cybercrime.gov.in%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1-1705500219.jpg%201296w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1-1705500219-300x183.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1-1705500219-500x305.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1-1705500219-768x469.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1-1705500219-150x92.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338451%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMurthy%20advises%20victims%20to%20report%20cyber%20complaints%20at%20cybercrime.gov.in%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20unfortunately%2C%20Murthy%20lost%20his%20phone%20while%20travelling%20to%20a%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20me%20two%20days%20to%20retrieve%20all%20my%20old%20data.%20I%20searched%20the%20same%20old%20app%20to%20pay%20the%20loan%20amount.%20But%20as%20it%20was%20an%20unauthorised%20app%2C%20it%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20Play%20Store.%20So%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20pay%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Murthy%20found%20out%20that%20the%20criminal%20had%20circulated%20his%20naked%20morphed%20images%20labelling%20him%20a%20%E2%80%98rapist%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98fraudster%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98kidnapper%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20trauma%20was%20so%20much%20that%20my%20phone%20would%20constantly%20ring%20as%20they%20continued%20to%20share%20my%20photos%20with%20all%20my%20contacts%20from%20different%20numbers.%20I%20was%20getting%20up%20to%201%2C300%20calls%20and%201%2C500%20broadcast%20messages%20in%20an%20hour.%20I%20lost%20my%20concentration%20on%20work.%20And%20I%20had%20already%20lost%20my%20dignity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20my%20hometown%2C%20my%20parents%20were%20mentally%20tortured%20by%20relatives%20and%20society.%20They%20are%20teachers%20by%20profession%2C%20so%20they%20were%20questioned%20for%20their%20teachings%20for%20other%20kids%20at%20school%20when%20their%20own%20son%20was%20%E2%80%98unethical%E2%80%99.%20I%20wanted%20to%20explain%20to%20everyone%20I%20was%20innocent%2C%20but%20my%20own%20parents%20did%20not%20believe%20me.%20I%20was%20getting%20depressed%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20one%20day%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20then-commissioner%20of%20police%20V%20C%20Sajjanar.%20A%20conversation%20with%20him%20gave%20Murthy%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20a%20victim%20to%20protecting%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20contacts%20were%20among%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%201%2C500%20contacts%2C%20he%20had%20also%20received%20similar%20messages%20from%20the%20criminal%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20narrated%20everything%20to%20him%2C%20I%20broke%20down.%20He%20mentored%20and%20motivated%20me%20to%20use%20my%20personal%20tragedy%20to%20help%20others.%20I%20realised%20if%20a%20person%20like%20me%20who%20had%20some%20knowledge%20of%20cybersecurity%20could%20become%20a%20victim%2C%20then%20what%20about%20young%20school%20and%20college-going%20students%3F%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murthy%20says%20that%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20then-commissioner%20of%20police%20V%20C%20Sajjanar%20gave%20him%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1705499518-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338445%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMurthy%20says%20that%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20then-commissioner%20of%20police%20V%20C%20Sajjanar%20gave%20him%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20onwards%2C%20Murthy%20started%20working%20on%20expanding%20his%20cybersecurity%20expertise.%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20I%20took%20a%20part-time%20job%20to%20manage%20my%20expenses.%20And%20then%20I%20started%20raising%20awareness%20on%20cyber%20security%20and%20crimes%20on%20social%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%2C%20Murthy%20understood%20that%20there%20is%20a%20large%20chain%20of%20criminals%20comprising%20minors%20who%20misuse%20the%20sim%20cards%20of%20elderly%20citizens%20to%20operate%20such%20applications.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20work%20from%20areas%20that%20are%20closer%20to%20border%20states.%20Sometimes%2C%20it%20becomes%20difficult%20to%20catch%20and%20arrest%20them%20under%20such%20circumstances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20started%20getting%20help%20requests%20from%20victims%2C%20he%20launched%20his%20company%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fglobalsecuritycouncil%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Security%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20to%20assist%20such%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20it%20works%2C%20Murthy%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20I%20counsel%20the%20victim%20as%20most%20of%20the%20time%20they%20end%20up%20having%20suicidal%20thoughts.%20After%20listening%20to%20my%20journey%2C%20they%20feel%20motivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20Murthy%20offers%20technical%20solutions.%20%E2%80%9CI%20check%20if%20their%20phone%20is%20hacked.%20I%20remove%20all%20the%20permissions%20from%20the%20fraudulent%20apps%20and%20protect%20data%20breaches.%20I%20advise%20them%20to%20change%20the%20phone%20number.%20In%20cases%20of%20harassment%20and%20defamation%2C%20I%20also%20help%20the%20victims%20find%20the%20locations%20of%20the%20criminals%20using%20IP%20addresses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurthy%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20has%20not%20only%20helped%20other%20victims%20but%20also%20helped%20him%20regain%20his%20identity%20and%20affection%20from%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20only%20after%20a%20year%20when%20my%20father%20finally%20understood%20me.%20He%20literally%20took%20me%20into%20his%20arms%20and%20broke%20down%20for%20having%20misunderstood%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murthy%20worked%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20cyber%20security%20volunteering%20force%20for%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-1-1705499553-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338446%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMurthy%20worked%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20cyber%20security%20volunteering%20force%20for%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20important%20steps%20for%20cybercrime%20victims%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20his%20own%20experience%2C%20Murthy%20offers%20five%20simple%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F81790%2Fdhanya-menon-cybercrime-investigation-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafeguard%20individuals%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20cybercrime%20and%20outlines%20essential%20steps%20that%20victims%20of%20cybercrime%20should%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Secure%20your%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20it%20is%20very%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20your%20data%20is%20secured.%20When%20you%20access%20any%20application%2C%20you%20do%20not%20just%20install%20the%20app%2C%20you%20give%20it%20access%20to%20your%20camera%2C%20contacts%2C%20Gmail%20account%2C%20and%20location.%20I%20suggest%20you%20install%20only%20very%20crucial%20apps%20and%20avoid%20giving%20them%20unnecessary%20access.%20Also%2C%20we%20must%20regularly%20check%20if%20our%20apps%20have%20any%20kind%20of%20access%20they%20should%20actually%20not%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMinimise%20the%20use%20of%20Gmail%20everywhere%20because%20if%20your%20phone%20is%20hacked%2C%20the%20hacker%20gets%20access%20to%20your%20phone%20and%20contacts%20because%20Gmail%20is%20linked%20to%20your%20contacts%20and%20gallery.%20Also%2C%20you%20must%20mask%20the%20camera%20on%20your%20laptop%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Change%20your%20privacy%20settings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20cybercrime%2C%20firstly%20your%20WhatsApp%20is%20compromised.%20So%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20ensure%20end-to-end%20encryption%20on%20WhatsApp.%20Also%2C%20many%20people%20do%20not%20know%20that%20they%20can%20choose%20%E2%80%98silence%20unknown%20callers%E2%80%99%20and%20protect%20their%20IP%20addresses%20by%20changing%20privacy%20settings.%20You%20must%20enable%20it%20to%20secure%20yourself%20from%20cybercriminals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Reboot%20your%20phone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179257%2Fmumbai-couple-troll-police-cyberbullying-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evictim%20of%20cybercrime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20you%20should%20first%20deactivate%20your%20WhatsApp%20account%20immediately%20and%20remove%20photos%20from%20the%20gallery.%20Thereafter%2C%20you%20must%20reboot%20your%20phone.%20This%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20hacker%20loses%20access%20to%20your%20data%20and%20all%20the%20apps%20are%20closed%20automatically%2C%E2%80%9D%20suggests%20Murthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20our%20work%2C%20we%20can%20trace%20the%20location%20but%20not%20the%20person.%20It%20is%20illegal.%20It%20is%20the%20police%20whom%20one%20should%20seek%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20harassment%20or%20defamation%20on%20social%20media%20verticals%20like%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Facebook%2C%20police%20write%20to%20their%20parent%20company%20Meta%20and%20report%20the%20profile.%20They%20will%20monitor%20their%20cookies%2C%20browsing%20history%2C%20and%20messages.%20So%2C%20not%20only%20will%20they%20find%20their%20location%20using%20the%20IP%20address%20but%20also%20identify%20the%20criminal.%20So%2C%20the%20right%20way%20is%20to%20approach%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Register%20your%20complaint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurthy%20advises%20victims%20to%20report%20cyber%20complaints%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcybercrime.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybercrime.gov.in%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20portal%20has%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20financial%20frauds%20and%20cybercrime%20related%20to%20women%20and%20children.%20It%20also%20allows%20victims%20to%20report%20a%20complaint%20anonymously%20as%20well.%20Here%2C%20you%20do%20not%20need%20to%20visit%20the%20police%20station%20every%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Radha%20Krishna%20Murthy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705502267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-2-1705499767.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D338444%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Radha%20Krishna